'''Pok-vu̍t-kón''' (博物館) fe̍t-chá '''pok-vu̍t-yen''' (博物院), he ôn-chṳ yit-tho vùn-vu̍t tién-chhông ke kien-chuk-vu̍t fe̍t-he kî-kèu.  
Pok-vu̍t-kón seu-chhông yî-khi̍p vì-fu khí -yû [[khô-ho̍k]], [[ngi-su̍t]] fe̍t-chá [[li̍t-sṳ́]] chhung-yeu-sin ke vu̍t-khien.

